Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.58,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,This is freaking amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.58,0:01:56.84,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Freaking?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.98,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some too, Ayane?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.04,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.44,0:02:02.79,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You have one too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.14,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to the new seating arrangements yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.81,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I have!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.46,0:02:15.35,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Winter break ended in January and we had another seating change.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.10,0:02:21.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It could just be my imagination, but the girl who sits behind me, Takahashi,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.31,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,jokes with me even during class,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.99,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,and the boy next to me, Yagi, starts conversations with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.75,Default,Yagi,0000,0000,0000,,I often get sleep paralysis.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.15,Default,Yagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that's normal? {en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sleep_paralysis, detail.chiebukuro.yahoo.co.jp/qa/question_detail/q1113561471}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.67,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, perfectly normal.
