Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.65,0:02:43.45,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like people aren't avoiding me as much.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.45,0:02:44.51,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.89,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to all of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.74,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Sawako, always too grateful.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.63,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,We might not be sitting next to each other now,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.91,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not like things have gone back to the way they were before we became friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.66,0:03:00.77,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, things only seem to be getting better.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.63,0:03:02.93,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Sawako?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.07,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.39,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.61,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No way, really?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it just like this!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.39,0:03:17.09,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it'd be a lie if I said things were perfect.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.42,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle, tickle!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.32,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Giggle, giggle?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{missing}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.57,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,She's become a lot brighter lately, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.94,0:03:38.76,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.60,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,No small thanks to Shota here, no doubt.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.60,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.69,0:03:52.53,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I had gotten a little bit closer to Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.33,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since we switched seats,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.70,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we've grown a little bit farther apart again.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.92,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's February.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.08,0:04:21.19,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really eat sweets, but if you want to give me something, I won't say no.
