Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.15,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And this one...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.30,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually maybe I shouldn't write him a card.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.39,0:05:41.38,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why does Kazehaya's bag seem to have more pieces with nuts than everyone else's?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.92,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And those pieces with hearts!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.32,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there so many hearts?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.85,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was I favoring him subconsciously?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.92,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And these are handmade, too...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.42,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to give him handmade chocolates...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.96,0:06:03.50,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe this is too much.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.72,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But I....
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.79,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,really want to
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.91,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,give them to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.06,0:06:40.87,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.55,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.43,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He just took chocolate out of his locker, didn't he?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.35,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course he did!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.57,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.02,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.74,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.04,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,These are so good!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Share them with Sanada, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.49,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.49,0:07:26.60,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.53,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.55,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at this.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.05,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you like them.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.60,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I have just one left.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I have chocolates for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.52,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.08,0:07:40.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.11,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Obligatory chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.17,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more, nothing less.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.77,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Look how happy that dork is though.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I need to use the restroom!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.12,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.20,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.76,0:08:04.97,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.61,0:08:09.88,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's been getting chocolates all morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.89,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,If I give him mine too, he'd have way too much chocolate.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.74,0:08:21.48,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he can't finish eating all of them today, he can refrigerate them!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.52,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,If I just give them to him casually and happily like she did,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.28,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he would be happy to take them too!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.55,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, chocolates for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.69,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's somehow even more awkward and unnatural.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.55,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.55,0:08:45.17,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can just give them to him normally, like I did with Ayane and Chizu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.04,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, normally?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.18,0:08:50.88,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.73,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.73,0:08:58.42,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I just keep over-thinking things when it comes to Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.76,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You got chocolates too, Ryu?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.85,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,This chocolate tastes different than the previous ones.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.85,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was okay for me to have one?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.17,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Were these more than just obligatory chocolates?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.72,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.66,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.71,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida made these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.41,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(0,3424,\fscx115\fscy125)\fs25\frz313.43\move(659,357,668,357,0,3424)}To Ryu
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.77,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.51,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma made them.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.49,0:09:30.86,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,So they're obligatory chocolates through Chizuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.01,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,S-She has the same chocolates!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.36,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Do you want one?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.24,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can have one.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.09,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.09,0:09:46.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's asking for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.95,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely over-thinking this.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.26,0:10:03.93,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,If we were still sitting where we were before,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.04,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,would I have been able to hand them out naturally?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.23,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like he turned her down.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, such a waste.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.20,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Turned her down?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.19,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Turned down her chocolates?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.84,0:10:49.04,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,So those weren't... obligatory chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.58,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, it was only selfishness and misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.05,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe the only reason he accepted the other chocolates so easily
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.80,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,was because they were just obligatory chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.72,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are out of thanks,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.05,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but does that make them obligatory chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:09.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB1AF9F&\frz25.338\pos(1030,326)}February 14th
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.45,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship chocolates?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.03,0:11:13.18,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to use them to confess to him!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.74,0:11:18.11,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't deny that I like him.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.17,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of chocolates are these?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.12,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like he turned her down.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.13,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That really woke me up.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.55,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give them to him so badly.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.27,0:11:46.05,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to hurry up, or else...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.79,0:11:50.14,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, s-school's over already?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.61,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hooked on this drama rerun right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.24,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Which one? A foreign drama?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.66,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, a trendy drama! {en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japanese_television_drama#Trendy_dramas huh.}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.32,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Did that girl ever manage to give him her chocolates?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.64,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.91,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Yano-chin, Sawako.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.69,0:12:14.91,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna stop somewhere before going home?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have to meet my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.21,0:12:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{missing}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.51,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's going to leave!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.42,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.55,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Have I got a job for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.62,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.08,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on home!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.82,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.42,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.94,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Because only you can do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.21,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He still hasn't left.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.94,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,This could be...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.88,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,my last chance.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I really...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.15,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could you guys go on without me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.40,0:13:03.80,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here for a little longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.31,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll stay with—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.89,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.02,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,We can go ahead. See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.69,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.99,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you noticed that he's been staring at you the whole time?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.15,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Don't look at him.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.95,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I did it. I'm here alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.84,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But now what?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.71,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.20,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulders have been really stiff lately.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.88,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a strong one, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.82,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you asked me to come here?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.18,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You should be honored.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.93,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you don't want to though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.93,0:13:56.26,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when you came to me crying in the middle of a storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:58.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1100,1000)\bord1.5\c&H4F8AC6&\pos(1107,474)\3c&H1E4D9B&}Eight year old\N Kazehaya
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.95,0:14:00.98,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy said to bring this to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.44,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Were you afraid of the storm?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.10,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when you said you wanted to sleep over at my house
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:10.37,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fad(700,1000)\pos(1135,446)\3c&H4533B8&\c&H9E8FED&}Six year old\NKazehaya
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.60,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,and you ended up wetting my bed?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.17,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yay...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.98,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kid!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.05,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should take a picture.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.05,0:14:18.37,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should broadcast all of these super interesting things over the school—
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright, I got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.30,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.08,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,My left shoulder and the back of my neck are especially sore.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.01,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Darn him.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.94,0:14:31.99,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What're those?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.05,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Those chocolates?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.05,0:14:38.56,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,When you're as awesome as I am, your fans just never leave you alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.54,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,He's so egotistical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:44.65,Choco Bags,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs23\fscy150\fscx170\c&H385050&\frz357.351\pos(633,488)}Thank you for all\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:44.69,Choco Bags,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs23\fscy140\fscx160\c&H385050&\frz357.351\pos(638,475)}Thank you for all\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:44.73,Choco Bags,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs23\fscy120\fscx140\c&H385050&\frz357.351\pos(636,460)}Thank you for all\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:44.78,Choco Bags,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs23\fscy110\fscx130\c&H385050&\frz357.351\pos(635,452)}Thank you for all\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:44.98,Choco Bags,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\fscy100\fscx120\t(\fscy80\fscx100)\c&H385050&\frz357.351\move(637,444,637,428,0,187)}Thank you for all\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.95,Choco Bags,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\c&H385050&\frz357.351\pos(638,428)}Thank you for all\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, those chocolates aren't from Kuronuma, are they?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.12,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.12,0:14:55.74,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd break the girl's heart by telling you who they were from!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.96,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're pitiful.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.49,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.36,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bone you're hitting!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.81,0:15:07.68,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the pain in your left shoulder and back of your neck are some sort of punishment?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.72,0:15:13.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I read in a manga once that problems from the neck and and above are caused by God.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.18,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,God?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.14,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm being punished for messing with sacred trees at shrines,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.87,0:15:25.34,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,or being stingy with offerings.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.21,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll purify myself with her chocolates!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.39,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.93,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,He choked.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.09,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water! Water!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.20,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to give these to him,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.69,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do it now!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.10,0:16:30.88,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.51,Alt,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.51,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.86,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.90,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you accept some chocolates from me since it's Valentine's Day?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.60,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.63,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the first and last time I ever give you any.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.64,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.77,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Spying on us?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.98,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.18,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.03,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I just got so caught up watching you two that I forgot to turn away.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.34,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,She admitted to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.96,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya doesn't accept homemade chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.85,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just give him?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.33,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's different. I'm special.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.94,0:18:03.42,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's already rejected me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.31,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm very special. Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.17,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are those for Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.57,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,They're a thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.57,0:18:26.27,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really just a thank you?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.49,0:18:32.27,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have any hidden meaning to them?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.81,0:18:43.39,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If those are just obligatory chocolates, I'm sure Kazehaya will gladly accept them.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.83,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't regret it now.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.98,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.40,0:18:57.50,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,She has no one to blame but herself if she backs off after being teased a little.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gotten any chocolates from you yet, Kurumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.29,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Really now?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She treats me like that even though we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's really changed lately, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.07,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,She was much cuter before.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think I like her better now.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.70,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You just like them cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.68,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are all cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is from class D, isn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.12,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sadako, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even a girl like her
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.69,0:19:46.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,wants to give out chocolates on Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.03,0:19:57.12,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Saying these are in thanks is just an excuse.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.69,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.94,0:20:09.36,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess I was really hoping for something today.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.53,0:20:15.22,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid because there's something I'm secretly hoping for.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.38,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If those are just obligatory chocolates, I'm sure Kazehaya would gladly accept them.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.17,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't obligatory chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.91,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,They definitely aren't.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.38,0:20:27.00,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I say they're a thank you,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.42,0:20:32.07,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but what I'm really thinking is...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.15,0:20:36.88,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What if they could bring us closer?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.42,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya doesn't accept homemade chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.14,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.50,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give them to him and pretend they're obligatory chocolates.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.77,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it. I mean it too much to give these to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.16,0:21:01.35,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't regret it now.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.69,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Those chocolates meant so much to me
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.91,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,that I couldn't give them to him.
