Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:33.89,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}The sun's set, the wind's blowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:38.68,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}furesouna kyouri
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:38.68,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}and we're so close that we can almost touch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:51.93,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kimi wo mitsumeteru zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:51.93,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}My gaze has always been fixed on you
